# Public API base URL consumed by the mobile app.
# Must include the /api suffix when the backend mounts routes under /api.
# In dev/staging, set this to the temporary HTTP URL exposed by Nginx.
# In production, switch to the HTTPS sub-domain (e.g. https://api.example.com/api).
